# Online Doctor Appointment Application вЂ” Implementation Plan

A full-stack, production-ready web application with responsive mobile-friendly design for booking doctor appointments online.

---

## Overview

A comprehensive healthcare appointment platform with three distinct user roles:
- **Patients** вЂ” Register, search doctors, book/manage appointments, leave reviews
- **Doctors** вЂ” Manage profiles, schedules, and patient appointments
- **Admins** вЂ” Full platform management, analytics, and content control

---

## Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|---|---|
| **Frontend** | Next.js 14 (App Router), React, TypeScript |
| **Styling** | Vanilla CSS with CSS Variables (blue/white healthcare theme) |
| **Backend** | Node.js + Express.js (REST API) |
| **Database** | SQLite (via better-sqlite3, for zero-config local dev) |
| **Auth** | JWT (access + refresh tokens), bcrypt password hashing |
| **Notifications** | In-app (database-driven), Nodemailer for email |
| **File Uploads** | Multer (doctor profile photos) |
| **Validation** | Zod (frontend + backend) |

> [!NOTE]
> SQLite is used for zero-configuration local development. The schema is fully compatible with PostgreSQL for production migration via a single config change.

