## Database Models

### Users (base auth table)
`id, email, password_hash, role (patient|doctor|admin), name, phone, avatar, created_at, is_active`

### Patients
`id, user_id, date_of_birth, gender, blood_group, address, medical_history, emergency_contact`

### Doctors
`id, user_id, specialty_id, qualification, experience_years, clinic_name, clinic_address, clinic_lat, clinic_lng, consultation_fee, bio, is_verified, rating, total_reviews`

### Specialties
`id, name, description, icon`

### Availability (weekly schedule)
`id, doctor_id, day_of_week (0-6), start_time, end_time, slot_duration_minutes, is_active`

### Appointments
`id, patient_id, doctor_id, specialty_id, date, time_slot, status (pending|confirmed|cancelled|completed|rescheduled), reason, notes, fee, created_at, updated_at`

### Reviews
`id, appointment_id, patient_id, doctor_id, rating (1-5), comment, created_at`

### Notifications
`id, user_id, type, title, message, is_read, related_id, created_at`

