## Key Features Implementation

### Search & Filter
Server-side filtering with query params: `specialty`, `location`, `min_fee`, `max_fee`, `date`, `rating`. Returns paginated results.

### Slot Availability Logic
Availability table defines weekly schedule. On booking request, system checks existing confirmed appointments for that doctor+date, removes taken slots, returns free ones.

### Role-Based Access Control
Three middleware guards: `requirePatient`, `requireDoctor`, `requireAdmin`. JWT payload contains `role` and `user_id`. Protected routes reject unauthorized roles with 403.

### Appointment Flow
`Pending в†’ Confirmed (doctor) в†’ Completed` or `Cancelled/Rescheduled` at any point. Each status change triggers a notification to both parties.

### Notifications
Created server-side on key events (booking, confirmation, cancellation, review). Frontend polls `/api/notifications` every 30 seconds and shows unread count on bell icon.

### Reviews & Ratings
Only available after appointment status = `completed`. Doctor's `rating` field updated via trigger/query after each new review.

